<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.10">
<l>kaṭalvaṇ ṇaṉkaṇṇaṉ viṇṇa varkaru māṇik kameṉa tāruyir</l>
<l>paṭava raviṉa ṇaikki ṭanta parañcu ṭarpaṇṭu nūṟṟuva</l>
<l>raṭava rumpaṭai maṅka vaivarkaṭ kāki veñcamat taṉṟutēr</l>
<l>kaṭavi yaperu māṉka ṉaikaḻal kāṇpa teṉṟukol kaṇkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ocean-coloured one, Kṛṣṇa, the black ruby of the celestials, my precious life,</l>
<l>the highest glow who lies on a hooded serpent bed, the great man who drove the chariot</l>
<l>that day in hot battle for the sake of the Five when [their] army diminished that came</l>
<l>so that the Hundred would die formerly, when will [my] eyes see his tinkling anklets?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
